Ọka bụ isi obodo Anambara steeti na-ekwo n'abalị abụọ nke ọnwa Novemba ihintuliaka onye ga-abụ Gọvanọ adịla nso.
Ndị Anambara ga-ebinye aka n'akwụkwọ onye ga-achị ha n'ụbọchị Satọde abalị isii nke ọnwa Novemba afọ 2021.
Nwalee etu ị ga-esi chekwa onwe gị na ntuliaka gọvanọ Anambra
Anambra Governorship Election 2021: Ipob, ndị'godfather',ego na ihe ndị ọzọ ga-ekwu onye ga-emeri na ntuliaka Anambra
Onye ntaakụkọ BBC Igbo gara ọdụ ụgbọala njem dị iche iche n'Ọka were hụ na ọtụtụ mmadụ sị Anambara na-apụ apụ n'ihi egwu ọgbaghara nwere ike ịdapụta ụbọchị ntuliaka ahụ.
Okporoụzọ na-ekwo ụbọchị Novemba 2, 2021 dịka ọtụtụ na-eme njem
Na Uni Zik Junction , otu nwoke na-eme njem aha ya bụ Geofrey Ugah kwuru na ya na-eme njem ahụ makana ha achọghị ị nọ n'Anambra site na 4th Nov ruo izu ụka n'abịa abịa.
Out onye ntorobịa anyị kwudoro ebe a na adọrọ ego bụ ATM kwuru na ya bịara iwere ego ugbua makana egwu dị na ngwa ngwa elekshiọn na atinye ụkwụ, ego nwere ike ịkọ ụkọ na Bankị.
Ntuliaka onye ga-achị Anambra ga afịọ ụbọchị satọde na-abịanụ.
Cheta na otu na-azọ nwere onwe bụ IPOB ekwuola ka onye ọbụla ghara ịpụta ezị site na 5th rue 10th nke ọnwa November.
Mana gọmenti ekwuola na ya bụ ntuliaka  ga-adịrịrị ụbọch Satọdee.
Unizik ga-emechi malite 4-9 ọnwa Novemba
Ebe foto si, Nnamdi Azikiwe University/Facebook
Ka nke a na-eme, Mahadum Nnamdi Azikiwe University  dị n'Ọka, Ekwuola na ha agaghị enwe agụmagwụkwọ malite n'abalị anọ rue abalị Itoolu nke nke ọnwa Novemba.
Nke a pụtara n'ihe n'akwụkwọ ozi nke ọnụ na-ekwurmahadum ahụ bụ Chika Gladys Ene ahụ binyere aka ma werpụta ụbọchị Tuzde, abalị abụọ nke ọnwa Novemba.
Mana ozi ahụ ekwughị ihe kpartara mechi nkuzi ahụ ha gbara ọkwa ya.
